<a href="https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1X_z2Lx8-C_1aCqiXSUgszFAn_R2c091u6-6Pf-Frk4c/edit?usp=sharing" title="Spreadsheet Data" target="_blank" class="limegreen">Spreadsheet Data</a>
</div>

<p>Variables to Include:</p>

<ul>
  <li>Full Name</li>
  <li>Constituency Name</li>
  <li>Province</li>
  <li>Constituency Telephone</li>
  <li>Constituency Fax</li>
  <li>Hill Telephone</li>
  <li>Hill Fax</li>
  <li>Individual’s photo</li>
</ul>
